citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12 pm on
09-Oct-19.
Went to facility and found no one home. Spoke to Mr. Wickey via telephone. Neither he nor Mrs. Wickey is
available for inspection today. Confirmed optimal hours for inspection.
